## üîß Tech Stack (All Free)

### AI/ML (Free Tiers)
- **Groq**: 7,000 free requests/day (faster than GPT-4)
- **Hugging Face**: Free inference API for image models
- **Vercel AI SDK**: Abstraction layer (free)

### Tools
- **Dexie.js**: IndexedDB wrapper
- **Papaparse**: CSV parsing
- **xlsx**: Excel handling
- **Fuse.js**: Fuzzy search
- **@react-pdf/renderer**: PDF generation
- **Sonner**: Toast notifications
- **Framer Motion**: Animations (optional)

### Testing (Free)
- **Vitest**: Faster than Jest
- **Playwright**: Better than Cypress for Next.js
- **MSW**: API mocking

---

## üì± Mobile Strategy (PWA-First)

### Why Not React Native Yet?
- PWA covers 80% of mobile needs
- Zero deployment cost (same Vercel hosting)
- Works offline with service workers
- Install to home screen on iOS/Android

### When to Build Native App?
- After 500+ farms (Phase 3)
- When you need:
  - Bluetooth for IoT devices
  - Background GPS tracking
  - Advanced camera features
  - Push notifications (can use web push until then)

