## üö® Free Tier Limits to Watch

| Service | Free Limit | When to Upgrade |
|---------|-----------|-----------------|
| Vercel | 100GB bandwidth | ~10K daily users |
| Clerk | 10K MAU | 2000 farms √ó 5 users |
| Firebase | 50K reads/day | Heavy reporting usage |
| Supabase | 2GB bandwidth | Large CSV exports |
| Resend | 100 emails/day | Critical alerts only |

**Pro Tip**: Use WhatsApp Business API (free via Twilio sandbox) instead of SMS for notifications. Pakistani farmers prefer WhatsApp anyway!

